text: Allison Williams (born April 13, 1988) is an American actress and comedian. She plays Marnie Michaels in the television drama Girls. She plays Jillian in The Mindy Project. Allison Williams was born in New Canaan, Connecticut. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Comedians from Connecticut Category:Actors from Connecticut Category:People from New Canaan, Connecticut Category:1988 births Category:Living people
